EditListingAvailabilityPanel.guide: Letting buyers know about your availability is an important part of creating a successful listing on SkillPickr. By updating your calendar regularly and being upfront about any conflicts or time off, you can help ensure that bookings are made with clear expectations on both sides. It's also a good idea to be responsive to messages and booking requests to maintain a positive reputation as a reliable and flexible seller. Showcasing your availability helps establish trust and confidence with potential buyers, leading to successful bookings on SkillPickr.

To get started, you'll need to fill out your first listing and complete all the necessary details. This includes information about what you are offering, pricing, and delivery details. By providing accurate and complete information, you can help ensure a smooth and successful transaction for both you and the buyer. If you need any help along the way, don't hesitate to reach out to us through the chat or at hello@skillpickr.dk. Get started today and take the first step towards receiving bookings on SkillPickr!

EditListingPhotosPanel.guide.selectPhoto: It's important to have a visually representative picture of you and your product, service or concept. This is where buyers will first get an impression of you, so make sure your image is clear, professional, and relevant to what you're offering. You can also upload additional photos to show more of your service, product, or work. Ensure that all photos are high-quality and give an accurate representation of what you're offering on SkillPickr. The first photo you upload will be your 'cover' photo, and once you've uploaded more, you can change the order using 'drag & drop'

EditListingPoliciesPanel.createListingDe: Creating your first listing on SkillPickr is an important step towards showcasing your skills and making them available to potential buyer. By creating a detailed listing, you will be able to effectively communicate what you have to offer and what sets you apart from other sellers. Once you create your first listing, you will have access to the Listing Manager, where you can manage all of your listings in one place and make updates as needed. With the Listing Manager, you will be able to streamline the process of creating and managing your listings, making it easier and more efficient to connect with potential clients. So start by creating your first listing today and unlock the power of the SkillPickr platform.
For help, reach out to us via the chat or at hello@skillpickr.dk - Regards, Allan and Cæcilie.

EditListingPricingForm.guide: Setting competitive and fair prices on SkillPickr is important to attract and retain customers. You have the flexibility to set your own pricing for your skills, services, concepts or products. Consider factors such as the time and resources required, market demand, and your own value when determining your prices. Keeping your prices updated and transparent will help establish credibility with buyers and increase your chances of getting booked. Make sure to review and adjust your prices regularly to ensure they align with your offerings and market conditions.

Purpose.how.text: By offering a large space for anyone to unleash their skills or passion and empower them to live a multi disciplinary creative life. By nurturing, inspiring and encouraging creative minds, help them find work with more ease and turn their skills into successful business. By making it easy for people to get in touch and book the skills of creative minds without speed bumps.
Purpose.how.title: How
Purpose.what.text: Based on a global tooling marketplace we work to support people living a multidisciplinary creative life by building tools that optimize their productivity, processes and workflow. This we do to help all creatives evolve their skill and make their business thrive, regardless of what level they are on. The marketplace also reduces the friction between users, saving time and money finding the right match.
Purpose.what.title: What
Purpose.why.text: Simply because we love and believe in people whose attitudes and approaches to problems and challenges bear the mark of creativity - of courage, of talent, of innovative problem solving

Teams.founding.allan: Allan has a background in design and software development, and has been involved in designing and implementing technological solutions for a number of companies. He is responsible for designing and implementing our technological solutions and ensuring that our products are up-to-date with the latest technology.
Teams.founding.antonio: Antonio is a professional business coach with many years of experience in coaching and developing business leaders. He serves as our business coach and helps us formulate our business strategy, set goals, and develop our leadership skills.
Teams.founding.cille: Cæcilie has a background in business development and project management, and has been involved in starting and growing several businesses. She is responsible for setting the direction for the company and ensuring that we meet our goals.
Teams.founding.text: As a team, we are working to revolutionize our industry by offering innovative solutions to our customers. In recent years, we have launched an MVP and have big plans for the future. Our goal is to become a leading player in our industry and continue to create value for our users, customers, and our team.
Teams.founding.title: SkillPickr Founding Team
Teams.mission.subTitle: We develop & create {breakline} a better world for creative artists.
Teams.mission.text: One place to brand, organize, keep track of jobs, payments and earn money for artistic people living a creative multidisciplinary life does not exist and for the customer, finding them is a time consuming and fragmented experience That is why Cæcilie, former PM and musician together with Allan, also former musician and UI specialist, launched SkillPickr in May 2022 with the mission to become a global online tooling marketplace and a community nurturing, inspiring and encouraging creative souls
